Interface CycleView

All Superinterfaces:
com.google.gwt.event.shared.HasHandlers, HasLoadHandlers, HasUnloadHandlers, LazyView
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseCycleView
public interface CycleView
extends LazyView, HasLoadHandlers, HasUnloadHandlers

Represent a view that can be injected to a CyclePresenter. Any class implementing this interface should fire LoadEvent and UnloadEvent when it is attached to/detached from the DOM.
